ConstructorArgumentKeys - Annotation Type in io.pivotal.rti.protocols
If the ProtocolAdapter implementation has constructor parameters and if the Spring auto-configuration mechanism is not used, then you must tag your constructor with ConstructorArgumentKeys annotation and provide keys that correspond to the parameters in the declaration order.
